  "title": "feat(carousel): introduce styling for all themes",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\n### [FX-2966](https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-2966)\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\nUltimately chose to put defaults in `reset.scss`, it may be sort of big relatively to the file but takes up less space than the range slider, and it's still small relative to the overall size of InstantSearch.\r\n\r\n- `reset` sets defaults for the carousel, it should be a grid with a horizontal scrollbar and centered buttons on each side on hover. Navigation buttons are unstyled.\r\n- Each theme then styles the buttons, and sets spacing and colors. I only used colors from their respective palettes.\r\n\r\n(I added red background and height to each item to make gaps and size obvious)\r\n`reset`:\r\n<img width=\"1152\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/7d2d67be-f682-476a-acb7-9c147b372055\">\r\n\r\n`algolia`:\r\n<img width=\"1152\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/6a261362-a4c6-453e-a773-46d4292f2e11\">\r\n\r\n`satellite`:\r\n<img width=\"1152\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a1f62cf9-4c09-4a10-a543-f2b728602e7f\">\r\n\r\n\n\n[FX-2966]: https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-2966?atlOrigin=eyJpIjoiNWRkNTljNzYxNjVmNDY3MDlhMDU5Y2ZhYzA5YTRkZjUiLCJwIjoiZ2l0aHViLWNvbS1KU1cifQ",
